{
  "texts": [
    "The planning module utilizes allocation policies to make scheduling decisions and analyzes the potential consequences of implementing changes in the system.The execution module utilizes actuators to perform resource scheduling on the Continuum infrastructure.",
    "It employs proactive scheduling policies for multi-objective optimization.",
    "The optimization objectives and trade-off parameters are implemented and stored in the Knowledge pool of the MAPE-K model.",
    "Resource scheduling algorithms can be utilized to update the rules within the Knowledge pool.",
    "The proactive scheduling algorithms make use of the models stored in the Knowledge pool to forecast the supplied amount of energy, including both green energy and brown energy, as well as the expected resource usage."
  ]
}